  <p id="title2-2"><i class="fa fa-tags color-red"></i>　<strong class="remarkable">② : Ruby on Rails 的安裝</strong></p>
  <br>
  <strong>
    呢么，咱們安裝 Ruby on Rails 吧！
    <br>
    这个有一点长，加油！
    <br><br>
    安裝的环境是
    <ul class="number_ul">
      <li><u>Ruby 2.1.3</u></li>
      <li><u>Ruby on Rails 4.2.6</u></li>
    </ul>
    <br>
    如果已经安裝好的话、<u>不用再安裝环境</u>。看<a href="#title2-3">下一個安裝</a>吧！
  </strong>
  <hr class="red-hr">
  <i class="fa fa-play-circle"></i>　<strong>我們先安裝叫做「<u>Command Line Tools</u>」的软件。</strong>
  <br><br>
  <i class="fa fa-exclamation"></i>　请准备好<strong><u>AppleID</u></strong>，用<strong><u>AppleID</u></strong><a href="https://developer.apple.com/downloads/index.action" target="_blank"><strong>从这里</strong></a>登录。
  <br>
  <small>※　注册AppleID<a href="https://support.apple.com/zh-cn/HT203993" target="_blank"><strong>请從这里做</strong></a></small>
  <br>
  <br>
  有下面一样的画面嗎？
  <%= link_to image_tag("https://s3-ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/coffee-cup/images/page2/Chrome_Apple_Developer.png",
                        :width => "90%",
                        :class => "hover_img textbook-title-img"),
              "https://s3-ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/coffee-cup/images/page2/Chrome_Apple_Developer.png",
              :target => ["_blank"] %>
  從这里安裝<strong>「<u>Command Line Tools</u>」</strong>。
  <hr class="red-hr">
  <i class="fa fa-arrow-right"></i>　<strong>安裝之前，先确认Mac的环境。</strong>
  <br>
  <small>※　随着Mac的环境，安裝的东西也不同。请注意。</small>
  <br><br>
  跟下面一樣子，点击 <i class="fa fa-apple"></i> ，之后点击里面的<strong>「<u>About This Mac</u>」</strong>。
  <%= link_to image_tag("https://s3-ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/coffee-cup/images/page2/Settiing_About_This_Mac.png",
                        :width => "90%",
                        :class => "hover_img textbook-title-img"),
              "https://s3-ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/coffee-cup/images/page2/Settiing_About_This_Mac.png",
              :target => ["_blank"] %>
  会显示下面的画面，请确认红线的地方。
  <%= link_to image_tag("https://s3-ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/coffee-cup/images/page2/About_This_Mac_Overview.png",
                        :width => "90%",
                        :class => "hover_img textbook-title-img"),
              "https://s3-ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/coffee-cup/images/page2/About_This_Mac_Overview.png",
              :target => ["_blank"] %>
  <%= link_to image_tag("https://s3-ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/coffee-cup/images/page2/About_This_Mac_Overview_detail.png",
                        :width => "90%",
                        :class => "hover_img textbook-title-img"),
              "https://s3-ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/coffee-cup/images/page2/About_This_Mac_Overview_detail.png",
              :target => ["_blank"] %>
  确认您 Mac 的环境之后，参考下面表下载「Command Line Tools」。
  <table class="table table-bordered table-hover" style="margin:15px 0">
    <thead style="font-size:15px">
      <tr>
        <td>Mac的环境</td>
        <td>Command Line Tools</td>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody style="font-size:12px">
      <tr>
        <td>10.11.x</td>
        <td>Command Line Tools(OS X 10.11)for Xcode x.x.x</td>
      </tr>
